{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":1,"day":25}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"打碎奴隶的枷锁","authors":["王彭年"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在非洲有个国家叫刚果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是个殖民主义的附属国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里的人民很善良，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿山、土地很肥沃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比利时统治足有几十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后来美国狼又在刚果插进了脚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"积极扩大来投资，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进行了残酷的抢劫和掠夺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"资本主义吸血鬼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丧尽了天良喝人血。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚果的人民吃不饱来穿不暖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"受尽了压榨和折磨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种族歧视不平等，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暗无天日苦难说。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成千上万无辜的百姓遭残害，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尸骨堆山血成河。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就是资本主义的“文明和自由”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就叫“大国帮小国”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唉！苦难的人民再也不能忍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奴隶的枷锁要挣脱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反帝斗争声势大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星火燎原燃烈火。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由独立的火炬高高举，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不受欺骗和压迫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"示威的队伍越来越大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女老幼紧跟着。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国的“后院”也起了风暴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涌澎湃气壮山河。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义的狰狞面目全暴露，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绞索越套越是紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃人的野兽要还血。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚果的人民是兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支援你，咱们六万万中国人民都有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"责。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界爱和平人民都支持，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利一定属于刚果。"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}